份文職 16k過日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n知自己未必做得長 盡早諗定仲有咩其他選擇<br />\n<br />\n利申18fg"},{"pid":"34c943f886483fbcebb3d06e4b46d871bd03e094","tid":975543,"uid":4000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T01:57:04.000Z","msg":"假MT算唔算MT<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d8f45a8bb0af920f99dbfc8f5bc2549279eea1","tid":975543,"uid":229095,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0f6b744a4760b1d79bf11400824e1e8041de1b8e","tid":975543,"uid":23782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T16:57:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:08:33.000Z","msg":"當初入到<span style=\"color: red;\">ive</span>，入到去讀書力不從心，gpa唔夠高(&lt; 3)，cv唔夠人勁，又無父幹無connection<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上個sem開始係fg搵工季節，知道自己唔會有啲咩mt offer，但本住報左都無壞既心態咩都報下。眼見身邊既朋友個個都有進展，又ac又剩，自己做完apt test vi果啲就收曬皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （已經有梳屎）有時同朋友傾起見到佢地滔滔不絕，但係我就站著如嘍囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有頭髮邊個想做幟哥，人人都想有offer架啦，但自己知自己事，心入面咪唯有安慰下自己其實做咩都無所謂，做mt都唔係好把炮姐。但見到周圍既人同自己咁大對比，大家都有曬planning有曬著落咁，真係會覺得自己好廢。<br />\n<br />\n對未來好迷惘，唔知自己可以有咩出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"953ac5bd56d7e287adcd4a60256d3b05b66619e3","tid":975543,"uid":23782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"31d541f62e11f9a675c618ec54c7562006aa80e5","tid":975543,"uid":103617,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T17:31:38.000Z","msg":"等下年big 4lol"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T02:13:04.000Z","ms